        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Ok.\r\n\r\nOne more potential edge case that may be worth thinking about:\r\n\r\n- client attaches with no root_dir\r\n- client is sent a `workspace/didChangeWorkspaceFolders` notification to add a workspace.\r\n- `set ft=...` triggers the client to attach again.\r\n\r\nEDIT: I've got a solution to this.",
